{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/blog/two-ball-colliding","webpackCompilationHash":"9ce4d8dcfa6af1529e7b","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"弹性碰撞与圆周率的计算","date":"Wed, 23rd October 2019","tags":["bubbles"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/621b27dfd8844499270320d2884bfc66/4148e/c44.png","srcSet":"/static/621b27dfd8844499270320d2884bfc66/4148e/c44.png 1x,\n/static/621b27dfd8844499270320d2884bfc66/de03e/c44.png 1.5x,\n/static/621b27dfd8844499270320d2884bfc66/1e9e2/c44.png 2x"}}}},"html":"<p>在理想模型下(没有任何阻力，弹性碰撞)，将一个静止小方块放在在墙壁和大方块之间，\n让大方块以一定的初始速度撞向小方块，那么小方块总共会碰撞几次呢？\n简单计算可以知道，当</p>\n<p>大方块质量为小方块一倍时，经过第一次碰撞加速后，小方块会在和墙壁来一次亲密接触后\n反弹并再次和大方块发生一次碰撞，所以小方块一共碰撞了3次。</p>\n<p>那么当大方块质量为小方块的100时呢？这时由于质量的巨大差别，小方块需要在墙壁和大方块之间\n往返多次才能大方块掉头远离。经过逐步计算可以知道这次小方块需要碰撞31次。</p>\n<p>那如果质量比变为10000倍呢？计算得知，倍感压力的小方块现在需要碰撞314次了。</p>\n<p>...</p>\n<p>发现规律了？</p>\n<p>没错，神奇的<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>π</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\pi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span></span></span></span>强势出现在次碰撞试验中了。</p>\n<p>查看视频可以有详细解答。\n====================  </p>\n<iframe height=500 width=100% src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=61421110&cid=106845214&page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"> </iframe>\n<p>====================  </p>","fields":{"slug":"two-ball-colliding"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"two-ball-colliding"}}}